media:group.media:title: Guns don’t kill but waitresses you don't tip do
media:group.media:description:
Anime: Akiba Maid War

This is what goes on behind closed doors when a new restaurant appears in the area you live in and forces the ones around it out of business. Imagine a world where all maids have concealed weapons permits.
